#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.stack.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.stack"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:1 of
msgid "Stack the prescribed level(s) from columns to index."
msgstr "将指定层级从列轴堆叠到索引轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:3 of
msgid ""
"Return a reshaped DataFrame or Series having a multi-level index with one"
" or more new inner-most levels compared to the current DataFrame. The new"
" inner-most levels are created by pivoting the columns of the current "
"dataframe:"
msgstr ""
"返回一个重塑后的 DataFrame 或 Series，其多级索引相对于当前 DataFrame 具有"
"一个或多个新的最内层级别。这些新的最内层级别是通过对当前 dataframe 的列"
"进行透视操作创建的："

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:8 of
msgid "if the columns have a single level, the output is a Series;"
msgstr "如果列只有一个层级，则输出为 Series；"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:9 of
msgid ""
"if the columns have multiple levels, the new index level(s) is (are) "
"taken from the prescribed level(s) and the output is a DataFrame."
msgstr "如果列具有多个层级，则新索引层级来自指定的层级，且输出为 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:13 of
msgid ""
"Level(s) to stack from the column axis onto the index axis, defined as "
"one index or label, or a list of indices or labels."
msgstr "要从列轴堆叠到索引轴的层级，定义为一个索引或标签，或索引或标签的列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:17 of
msgid ""
"Whether to drop rows in the resulting Frame/Series with missing values. "
"Stacking a column level onto the index axis can create combinations of "
"index and column values that are missing from the original dataframe. See"
" Examples section."
msgstr ""
"是否删除结果 Frame/Series 中包含缺失值的行。将列层级堆叠到索引轴可能会"
"产生在原始 dataframe 中缺失的索引和列值组合。参见示例部分。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:24 of
msgid "Stacked dataframe or series."
msgstr "堆叠后的 dataframe 或 series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.unstack`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:30 of
msgid "Unstack prescribed level(s) from index axis onto column axis."
msgstr "将指定层级从索引轴展开到列轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.pivot`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:33 of
msgid "Reshape dataframe from long format to wide format."
msgstr "将 dataframe 从长格式重塑为宽格式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.pivot_table`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:36 of
msgid "Create a spreadsheet-style pivot table as a DataFrame."
msgstr "创建一个类似电子表格的透视表作为 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:39 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:40 of
msgid ""
"The function is named by analogy with a collection of books being "
"reorganized from being side by side on a horizontal position (the columns"
" of the dataframe) to being stacked vertically on top of each other (in "
"the index of the dataframe)."
msgstr ""
"该函数的命名是类比于一组书籍从水平并排的位置（dataframe 的列）重新组织成"
"垂直堆叠在一起（dataframe 的索引中）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:47 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:48 of
msgid "**Single level columns**"
msgstr "**单层列**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:55 of
msgid "Stacking a dataframe with a single level column axis returns a Series:"
msgstr "对具有单层列轴的 dataframe 进行堆叠操作将返回一个 Series："

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:68 of
msgid "**Multi level columns: simple case**"
msgstr "**多层列：简单情况**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:76 of
msgid "Stacking a dataframe with a multi-level column axis:"
msgstr "对具有多层级列轴的 dataframe 进行堆叠操作："

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:90 of
msgid "**Missing values**"
msgstr "**缺失值**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:98 of
msgid ""
"It is common to have missing values when stacking a dataframe with multi-"
"level columns, as the stacked dataframe typically has more values than "
"the original dataframe. Missing values are filled with NaNs:"
msgstr ""
"在对具有多层级列的 dataframe 进行堆叠时，通常会出现缺失值，因为堆叠后的 "
"dataframe 通常比原始 dataframe 包含更多的值。缺失值将用 NaN 填充："

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:115 of
msgid "**Prescribing the level(s) to be stacked**"
msgstr "**指定要堆叠的层级**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:117 of
msgid "The first parameter controls which level or levels are stacked:"
msgstr "第一个参数控制要堆叠的层级："

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:132 of
msgid "**Dropping missing values**"
msgstr "**删除缺失值**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.stack.stack:138 of
msgid ""
"Note that rows where all values are missing are dropped by default but "
"this behaviour can be controlled via the dropna keyword parameter:"
msgstr ""
"请注意，默认情况下所有值都缺失的行会被删除，但此行为可以通过 dropna "
"关键字参数来控制："

